  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You invoke the power of Hadar, the Dark Hunger. Tendrils of dark energy erupt from you and batter all creatures within 10 feet of you.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage but suffers no other effect.</p>\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes 2d6 points of bludgeoning damage and cannot use reactions until its next turn.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"hang\"><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 1d6.</p>"
